            <div type="transcript" id="J741">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Drama's Vitallest Expression is the Common Day</l>
                    <l>That arise and set about Us --</l>
                    <l>Other Tragedy</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Perish in the Recitation --</l>
                    <l>This -- the <app type="revision"><lem>more exert</lem><rdg>more exert</rdg></app>
best enact</l>
                    <l>When the Audience is scattered</l>
                    <l>And the Boxes shut --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>"Hamlet" to Himself were Hamlet --</l>
                    <l>Had not Shakespeare wrote --</l>
                    <l>Though the "Romeo" <app type="revision"><lem>leave</lem><rdg>leave</rdg></app>
left no Record</l>
                    <l>Of his Juliet,</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>It were <app type="revision"><lem>tenderer --</lem><rdg>tenderer --</rdg></app>
infinite enacted</l>
                    <l>In the Human Heart --</l>
                    <l>Only Theatre recorded</l>
                    <l><app type="revision"><lem>Never yet was shut --</lem><rdg>Never yet was shut --</rdg></app>
Owner cannot shut --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                </lg>

